# Disaster + Donation Features - Complete

## New APIs Created

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/api/campaigns` | GET/POST | List/create fundraising campaigns |
| `/api/donations` | GET/POST | Process donations (demo auto-complete) |
| `/api/teams` | GET/POST | List/create volunteer teams |
| `/api/volunteer/activations` | GET/PATCH | Get team disaster activations |

